<br>
Souls of Defiance has strong ties with Firestormers.  Their current Assistant Guildleader was GL of SoD when I joined.  Many of their members are former SoD members and we consider them (just like LoLF and LoOF) to still be family.  They have repeatedly extended courtesys to one of my officers and I am extending that courtesy back.<br>
<br>
Looking at the list i have so far we have 4 guests.  Deanna from LoOF, Blodiron from Blood and Iron (a federation applicant), Thetaghost from Firestormers and Mealon again from LoOF.  I do not see how these 4 people being included in the raid can be anything but a benefit to Federation members if it enables the raid to happen.  These are uber ( and people who know me know how I detest that word) items.<br>
<br>
This is a Federation Raid because it is organized by a Federation Officer and attended by Federation Members and friends.  Not Tritons are here. Noone from Rising Assention, Inverse Logic or Vhe'lores.  We did not open the raid to the Arbiters of the Apocolypse or Blades of Law.  This is a Federation Raid and I am following Federation Rules on Raiding.<br>
<br>
This is my reasoning in inviting Firestormers, LoOf, LoLF and B&amp;I.<br>
<br>
VonAlbrecht Jaeger<br>
Guildleader Souls of Defiance<br>
