<br>
And as to HoT, armor drops rates on average are 1-3. It takes a minimum of 2-3 groups if everyone is 58+. 4-5 groups otherwise. Heck I've even heard of a few single grps there all 60+. Sure some fights are tough, but it's not that bad. There is a much better loot distribution than from an epic mob. Inviting low level 50's are risky because of their resists, resist checks to mobs, and their overall experience with the style of raiding in HoT. It's great you are organizing events Von, I hope there's many more to come. I am just voicing my opinion as on older member of the Fed and seasoned HoT raider.<br>
